title: Babar Heir and Author Laurent de Brunhoff Dies Aged 98
description: 'Babar' author Laurent de Brunhoff, who revived his father's popular picture book series about an elephant king, has died.

title: Blake Lively Leads Apologies For Kate Middleton Jokes After Cancer Diagnosis Reveal
description: Kate Middleton's cancer diagnosis news has prompted some to express remorse about jokes made amid the public frenzy before her announcement.

title: Biden Signs $1.2 Trillion Funding Package After Senate’s Passage Ends Shutdown Threat
description: President Joe Biden on Saturday signed a $1.2 trillion package of spending bills after Congress had passed the long overdue legislation.

title: Rain Helps Contain Still-Burning Virginia Wildfires as State Sends More Aid
description: “Without a doubt the rain is helping" said Cory Swift, a spokesperson for the Virginia Department of Forestry.

title: Russia Detains 11 In Attack on Moscow Concert Hall That Killed at Least 115
description: Russian President Vladimir Putin said Saturday that authorities have detained 11 people in the fatal attack on a Moscow concert.

title: Olivia Munn Sends Message of Support to Fellow Cancer Sufferer Kate Middleton
description: Kate Middleton received a message of support from actor Olivia Munn, who recently opened up about her own cancer diagnosis.
